title: Art of Oceania, Africa and the Americas, Museum of Primitive Art
description:
Art of Oceania, Africa, and the Americas from The Museum of Primitive Art
NY Graphic Society | 1969 | 0870990438 | English | PDF | 270 pages | 23.7 Mb

The works in this exhibition come from many places and differ in many ways: in their materials and techniques, in the circumstances of their production and use, in their social and symbolic roles, in their craftsmanship, size, appearance, and style.
